data.description: Beautifull five bedroom, four bath pool home is the perfect turn-key short term rental. Warm painted walls greet you when you open the front door. The cozy living room is spacious with plenty of room for even the largest family and friends gatherings. A large archway opens to the well-appointed décor of the dining room and kitchen. Beautiful wood cabinets in the kitchen provide lots of storage. A kitchen island provides extra seating and creates a great place to gather while cooking. Two master suites are hard to find and this is one of them! Two additional bedrooms with twin beds in each provide extra beds for little ones with family friendly decor. Never hear the hear the words, I am bored, with a full game room including pool table, foosball table, tv, and table with chairs for hanging out. Cool off after a long day at Disney in the sparking pool that is waiting to be enjoyed. Sit poolside for an evening dinner or host a backyard cookout. Enjoy all the Disney Parks, Universal, Seaworld, restaurants to please all the family members, or terrific shopping are just minutes away.
